Lyakhov et al., focus on ODE, and properties of the\nso-called derived sub-algebra of the (finite) dimensional Lie algebra of\nsymmetries of the ODE. We also illustrate the powerful maximal symmetry groups\nfacility as a natural tool to be used in conjunction with MapDE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 9 Mar 2019 03:23:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Dec 2019 21:19:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-01"}
