eptibility maps in near real-time on routine computational hardware. This\npreliminary study establishes ASPEN's parity with existing approaches for\nquantitative accuracy on a well-curated gold standard dataset and further\ndemonstrates its robustness to streaking artifacts across a large cohort of\nsubjects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Mar 2019 21:49:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Mar 2019 01:20:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-14"}
